import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Homepage from './Routes/Homepage/Homepage.js'

ReactDOM.render(
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
        <Route path='/' element={<Homepage />} />
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>,
    document.getElementById('root')
)
